%% 图5-6 能力评估流程时序图
%% Figure 5-6 Sequence Diagram of Capability Assessment Process

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 用户
    participant FE as 前端 (React)
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>/assess
    participant IP as input_parser<br/>Agent
    participant DAs as 6 个维度 Agent<br/>(并发)
    participant SA as summary_agent
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant RA as 6 个报告 Agent

    U->>FE: 提交简历 + 自述 + (可选)测评
    FE->>API: POST /assess
    API->>DB: 创建 assessment_jobs<br/>(status=running)
    API->>IP: 调用 input_parser
    IP-->>API: 候选人结构化 JSON

    Note over API,DAs: 字段级裁剪后并发调度<br/>asyncio.gather(*tasks, return_exceptions=True)
    par 6 个维度 Agent 并发
        API->>DAs: skills_agent
        DAs-->>API: 4 子维度 + overall_score
    and
        API->>DAs: knowledge_agent
        DAs-->>API: 4 子维度 + overall_score
    and
        API->>DAs: abilities_agent
        DAs-->>API: 3 子维度 (done/locked)
    and
        API->>DAs: work_styles_agent
        DAs-->>API: 4 子维度 / 21 特质
    and
        API->>DAs: interests_agent
        DAs-->>API: RIASEC 6 类型 + 三字母代码
    and
        API->>DAs: work_values_agent
        DAs-->>API: 6 子维度
    end

    API->>DB: 写入 assessment_dimensions × 6
    API->>SA: 调用 summary_agent
    SA-->>API: persona_label + narrative<br/>+ top3_strengths + top3_improvements
    API->>DB: 写入 assessment_summary<br/>更新 assessment_jobs (status=done)
    API-->>FE: 返回 assessment_id

    Note over U,RA: 用户查看报告时按需生成 (惰性 + 缓存)
    U->>FE: 进入报告页
    FE->>API: GET /report/{assessment_id}
    API->>DB: 查 assessment_report_blocks
    alt 缓存命中
        DB-->>API: 已有 9-10 条 block_json
    else 首次生成
        par 6 个维度报告 Agent 并发
            API->>RA: render dimension_skills
            API->>RA: render dimension_knowledge
            API->>RA: render dimension_abilities
            API->>RA: render dimension_work_styles
            API->>RA: render dimension_interests
            API->>RA: render dimension_work_values
        end
        RA-->>API: 第二人称叙述 + 星级评分
        API->>DB: UPSERT assessment_report_blocks
    end
    API-->>FE: 返回报告 JSON
    FE-->>U: 渲染雷达图 + 维度详情
